          },
          "page_index": 0,
          "confidence": 0.8,
          "backend": "heuristic",
          "text_content": "• We show that reliable recomputation target selection requires an inference-consistent RoPE ordering , and introduce a global positional reconstruction of retrieved chunks to enable stable and meaningful token ranking.",
          "source_block_ids": [
            "c3e12812c628"
          ]
        },
        {
          "region_id": "ce94567d18d4",
          "region_class": "list",
