            "y1": 592.6394653320312
          },
          "page_index": 1,
          "confidence": 0.8,
          "backend": "heuristic",
          "text_content": "We consider an autoregressive Transformer decoder. Let h ℓ t ∈ R d denote the hidden state at layer ℓ and position t . For each attention head, keys and values are computed as linear projections of the hidden states,",
          "source_block_ids": [
            "f855b5544fdf"
          ]
        },
        {
          "region_id": "d6dbf5af615b",
          "region_class": "paragraph",
