          "page_index": 2,
          "confidence": 0.8,
          "backend": "heuristic",
          "text_content": "Thus, chunk reordering leverages the freedom in chunk or- dering to further align RoPE geometry with information flow in the decoding phase, complementing token selection under chunk-wise prefilling. More details on KV recompu- tation implementation can be found at Appendix. B",
